{"Name":"Sushant Singh Rajput","DateOfBirth":"1986-01-21","BirthPlace":"Patna, Inda","Description":  "Sushant Singh Rajput was an Indian television and movie actor who is best remembered for his work in the then-popular show Pavitra Rishta, where he played the role of Manav Deshmukh. He was associated with the show from 2009 to 2011, after which he bagged the role in Abhishek Kapoor`s Kai Po Che! in 2013, for which he won a Filmfare Award nomination for Best Debut and three awards in the same category. Over the years he went on to appear in several movies, a promising beginning for his career as an actor. On 14th June 2020, the talented actor met his untimely demise.","Movies":[{"Id":"mXi1UXgBtHd0Ifm6DFo3","Name":"Dil Bechara"}]}
