{"Name":"Rowan Atkinson","DateOfBirth":"1955-01-06","BirthPlace":"Consett, Durham, United Kingdom","Description":  "Rowan Atkinson is an English actor, comedian, and screenwriter who is best known as Mr. Bean. His career took off on the small screen with the BBC comedy sketch show Not the Nine O`Clock News, after which he bagged prominent roles in numerous sitcoms, reality shows and films. He gained worldwide recognition with his role as the bumbling Mr. Bean, a character he created himself which went on to get a TV show and a film series.Some of his most notable credits include films like Bean (1997), Scooby-Doo (2002), Johnny English (2003), Love Actually (2003), Keeping Mum (2005), Mr. Bean`s Holiday (2007), Johnny English Reborn (2011) and Johnny English Strikes Again (2018).","Movies":[{"Id":"m3i1UXgBtHd0Ifm6DFoi","Name":"Mr Bean"}]}

